company.tagline: Building Large World Models to perceive, generate, and interact with the 3D world.
company.description: World Labs is a spatial intelligence AI company building Large World Models (LWMs) to perceive, generate, and interact with the 3D world. The company aims to lift AI models from the 2D plane of pixels to full 3D worlds - both virtual and real - endowing them with spatial intelligence as rich as our own.
company.target_customers: Artists, designers, developers, engineers, and anyone looking to create their own worlds using generative AI.
